TEXT(&beginproblem);
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a = random(1,4,1);
$b = random(2,6,1);
$m = $b*exp($a);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));

Find the equation of the line tangent to the graph of \(y=$b e^x\)
at \(x=$a\).

$BR $BR

Tangent Line: \(y = \) \{ans_rule(30) \}
$BR

EOT

$ans = "$m*(x-$a)+$m";
&ANS(function_cmp($ans,"x"));

